  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>The jetpack exhaust is augmented with an atlantideum filter. When activated, its discordant effect is spilled across the landscape, a trail of dissonant reverberations that echo on an unknowable frequency.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>喷气背包的排气口上安装了一个亚特拉迪姆过滤器。启动背包后，这种物质的不谐效果就会挥洒在身后的大地上，并留下在未知频率上不断回响的刺耳尾迹。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>噴射背包排氣管使用亞特蘭提德鋼過濾器強化。啟動噴射器後，不和諧效果會噴灑在大地上，一條不和諧的殘響尾跡以不可知的頻率迴盪著。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
  },
